sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant App
    participant Geofence
    participant Bluetooth
    participant SwitchBot

    User->>App: Approaches home
    App->>Geofence: Check location
    Geofence-->>App: Entered boundary
    App->>Bluetooth: Start scan
    Bluetooth-->>App: Device found
    App->>SwitchBot: Authenticate + send open command
    SwitchBot-->>App: Command accepted
    App-->>User: Prompt open door available
